name: Beru Stew
Lore: 'Moisture farmers grow enough food to sustain Tatooine''s population. Beru Lars has devised many dishes using herbs and roots naturally found in Tatooine''s desert.',
Text: 'Each player must immediately activate 2 Force. Also, you may activate 1 additional Force for each Beru Lars, Owen Lars or Hydroponics Station on table.',
